{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01QoqVSGcnN7kjgZvX2x43zk","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t/**\n2\t * Hono environment type augmentation for custom context variables.\n3\t *\n4\t * userId: set by JWT middleware (from token sub claim).\n5\t * Wallet is NOT in context — routes that need wallet resolve it from the player profile.\n6\t */\n7\t\n8\texport type AppEnv = {\n9\t  Variables: {\n10\t    userId: string;\n11\t  };\n12\t};\n13\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":"toolu_01WnnsxD6PGcCqynR9abaSne","session_id":"59720d7a-048c-45e3-b4dd-63ce0cb4da31","uuid":"21147680-d0cd-49ee-a413-a831fdf1ed48","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:42:32.203Z"}
