{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01JdQuGjXRPpkWLbNTnG6YkG","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have a comprehensive understanding. Let me compile a detailed summary of the database schema and seed data:\n\n## Challenge Engine Database Schema & Seed Data Summary\n\nBased on the migration file `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` and handler implementations, here's the complete picture:\n\n---\n\n### **TABLE SCHEMAS**\n\n#### **1. Core Campaign & Challenge Tables**\n\n**`campaigns`** — Container for challenge groupings\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `name`: TEXT UNIQUE (e.g., \"Daily Challenges\", \"Weekly Challenges\", \"Onboarding\")\n- `campaign_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('daily', 'weekly', 'onboarding', 'dogpile')\n- `starts_at`, `ends_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (NULL = always active)\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n- `config`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' (type-specific settings)\n\n**`challenges`** — Template definitions for individual challenge tasks\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `title`: TEXT (e.g., \"Play 3 Games\", \"Win a Coinflip\")\n- `description`: TEXT\n- `action`: TEXT (e.g., 'game_completed', 'game_won', 'lobby_filled') — **maps to verification adapters**\n- `scope`: TEXT DEFAULT 'any' CHECK IN ('any', 'coinflip', 'lord', 'closecall') — **game-type filter**\n- `condition`: TEXT DEFAULT 'count' CHECK IN ('count', 'unique_game_types', ...)\n- `threshold`: INT — target value to meet\n- `reward_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'crate')\n- `reward_amount`: INT (for points) or NULL (for crates)\n- `prerequisite_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES challenges(id) — **for onboarding chain linking**\n- `eligible_if`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' (M2+ feature for eligibility rules)\n- `sort_order`: INT DEFAULT 0 — **used to select top 3 daily/top 2 weekly**\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n\n#### **2. Challenge Assignment (Per-Player Period Tracking)**\n\n**`challenge_assignments`** — Player's assignment for a challenge in a specific period\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `challenge_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES challenges(id)\n- `period_key`: TEXT NOT NULL — **date-scoped identifier (see below)**\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'active' CHECK IN ('active', 'completed', 'expired')\n- `progress`: INT DEFAULT 0 — current count toward target\n- `target`: INT NOT NULL — copied from challenge.threshold at assignment time\n- `assigned_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- `expires_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (NULL for onboarding)\n- `completed_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (when status becomes 'completed')\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, challenge_id, period_key)** — one assignment per player per challenge per period (idempotency guard)\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `idx_assignments_active` ON (user_id, status) WHERE status='active' — **hot query for game.settled**\n- `idx_assignments_period` ON (period_key, status)\n\n#### **3. Progress Tracking**\n\n**`progress_events`** — Audit trail of which game sessions contributed to challenge progress\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `assignment_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES challenge_assignments(id)\n- `round_id`: TEXT NOT NULL — match_id from game.settled event\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `progress_delta`: INT DEFAULT 1 — increment amount\n- `metadata`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' — context (e.g., `{\"game\":\"coinflip\"}`)\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(assignment_id, round_id)** — **idempotency: same round can't count twice**\n\n#### **4. Completion Bonus (Meta-Quest)**\n\n**`completion_bonuses`** — \"Complete all challenges in a period → bonus reward\"\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `title`: TEXT (e.g., \"Daily Bonus Crate\")\n- `description`: TEXT\n- `required_count`: INT (e.g., 3 = \"complete 3 daily challenges\")\n- `reward_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'crate')\n- `reward_amount`: INT (if reward_type='points')\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n\n**`bonus_completions`** — Per-player bonus completion record\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `bonus_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES completion_bonuses(id)\n- `period_key`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `completed_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, bonus_id, period_key)** — **idempotency: award bonus once per period**\n\n#### **5. Points & Rewards**\n\n**`player_points`** — Running balance of points earned by player\n- `user_id`: TEXT PRIMARY KEY\n- `wallet`: TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE\n- `balance`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — current spendable points\n- `lifetime_earned`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — monotonic aggregate\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`point_grants`** — Immutable ledger of all points awarded\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`, `wallet`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `source_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('wager', 'challenge_completed', 'bonus_completed', 'crate_points')\n- `source_id`: TEXT NOT NULL (round_id, assignment_id, bonus_id, or crate_id)\n- `amount`: BIGINT NOT NULL\n- `metadata`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' \n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, source_type, source_id)** — **idempotency key**\n\n**`reward_config`** — Operator-tunable economy parameters\n- `key`: TEXT PRIMARY KEY\n- `value`: TEXT NOT NULL (JSON-encoded)\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`reward_pool`** — Singleton accounting ledger for SOL crate funding\n- `id`: INT PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT 1 (singleton, only one row allowed)\n- `balance_lamports`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — available for SOL crate payouts\n- `lifetime_funded`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — total fees allocated → pool\n- `lifetime_paid`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — total SOL paid out via crates\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`reward_pool_fundings`** — Idempotent pool funding ledger\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `round_id`: TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE — **one record per settled round**\n- `fee_lamports`: BIGINT NOT NULL (platform fee collected)\n- `funded_lamports`: BIGINT NOT NULL (amount added to pool: fee * fee_share)\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n#### **6. Crate Drops**\n\n**`crate_drops`** — Random loot drop records\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `trigger_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('game_settled', 'challenge_completed', 'bonus_completed')\n- `trigger_id`: TEXT NOT NULL (round_id, assignment_id, or bonus_id)\n- `crate_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'sol')\n- `contents_amount`: TEXT NOT NULL (lamports or points as string)\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'pending' CHECK IN ('pending', 'granted', 'failed')\n- `created_at`, `granted_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `idx_crate_drops_user` ON (user_id, created_at DESC)\n- `idx_crate_drops_pending` ON (status) WHERE status='pending'\n\n#### **7. Anti-Abuse & Events**\n\n**`fraud_flags`** — Manual review queue for suspicious activity\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`, `flag_type`, `related_id`: TEXT\n- `details`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}'\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'open' CHECK IN ('open', 'reviewed', 'dismissed')\n- `created_at`, `resolved_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ\n\n**`dogpile_events`** — Limited-time point multiplier events\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `starts_at`, `ends_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n- `multiplier`: NUMERIC(4,2) DEFAULT 2.0\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'scheduled' CHECK IN ('scheduled', 'active', 'ended', 'cancelled')\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**Index:** `idx_dogpile_active` ON (status, starts_at, ends_at) WHERE status IN ('scheduled', 'active')\n\n---\n\n### **SEED DATA**\n\n#### **1. `reward_config` Defaults**\n```\npoints_per_dollar:          '500'        (e.g., $1 wagered = 500 points)\ndogpile_default_multiplier: '2.0'\nreward_pool_fee_share:      '0.20'       (20% of fees → pool)\npoints_crate_drop_rate:     '0.05'       (5% chance per game)\nsol_crate_drop_rate:        '0.01'       (1% chance per game)\nsol_crate_pool_pct:         '0.10'       (payout = 10% of pool balance)\nsol_crate_min_value:        '10000000'   (100M lamports = ~0.1 SOL threshold)\npoints_crate_min:           '500'\npoints_crate_max:           '5000'\ndaily_challenge_count:      '3'\nweekly_challenge_count:     '2'\n```\n\n#### **2. `campaigns` Seed**\n| id (auto) | name | campaign_type | starts_at | ends_at | is_active |\n|-----------|------|---------------|-----------|---------|-----------|\n| 1 | Daily Challenges | daily | NULL | NULL | true |\n| 2 | Weekly Challenges | weekly | NULL | NULL | true |\n| 3 | Onboarding | onboarding | NULL | NULL | true |\n\n#### **3. `challenges` Seed — Daily Campaign (campaign_id=1)**\n\nCampaigns has 6 daily challenge templates. Top 3 by `sort_order` are assigned to players each day:\n\n| Title | Action | Scope | Condition | Threshold | Reward | sort_order |\n|-------|--------|-------|-----------|-----------|--------|-----------|\n| Play 3 Games | game_completed | any | count | 3 | 100 points | 1 |\n| Win a Coinflip | game_won | coinflip | count | 1 | 150 points | 2 |\n| Fill a Lobby | lobby_filled | any | count | 1 | 200 points | 3 |\n| Play 5 Games | game_completed | any | count | 5 | 250 points | 4 |\n| Win 3 Games | game_won | any | count | 3 | 300 points | 5 |\n| Try Close Call | game_completed | closecall | count | 1 | 150 points | 6 |\n\n**Daily Completion Bonus (campaign_id=1):**\n- required_count: 3, reward_type: 'crate'\n\n#### **4. `challenges` Seed — Weekly Campaign (campaign_id=2)**\n\n6 weekly challenge templates. Top 2 by `sort_order` are assigned per week:\n\n| Title | Action | Scope | Condition | Threshold | Reward | sort_order |\n|-------|--------|-------|-----------|-----------|--------|-----------|\n| Play 20 Games | game_completed | any | count | 20 | 1000 points | 1 |\n| Win 10 Games | game_won | any | count | 10 | 1500 points | 2 |\n| Play Every Game Type | game_completed | any | unique_game_types | 3 | 2000 points | 3 |\n| Fill 5 Lobbies | lobby_filled | any | count | 5 | 1200 points | 4 |\n\n#### **5. `challenges` Seed — Onboarding Campaign (campaign_id=3)**\n\n3-step chain linked via `prerequisite_id`:\n\n**Step 1 (sort_order=1, prerequisite_id=NULL):**\n- Title: \"Play Your First Game\"\n- Action: game_completed, Scope: any, Threshold: 1, Reward: 1000 points\n\n**Step 2 (sort_order=2, prerequisite_id=Step1.id):**\n- Title: \"Win a Game\"\n- Action: game_won, Scope: any, Threshold: 1, Reward: 1500 points\n\n**Step 3 (sort_order=3, prerequisite_id=Step2.id):**\n- Title: \"Try All 3 Game Types\"\n- Action: game_completed, Scope: any, Condition: unique_game_types, Threshold: 3, Reward: 2500 points\n\n#### **6. `reward_pool` Seed**\n```\nINSERT INTO reward_pool (id, balance_lamports, lifetime_funded, lifetime_paid)\nVALUES (1, 0, 0, 0);\n```\n\n---\n\n### **PERIOD_KEY FORMAT & EXPIRATION**\n\nFrom integration tests, the `period_key` structure is:\n\n1. **Daily Challenges**: `\"daily:YYYY-MM-DD\"` (e.g., `\"daily:2026-04-03\"`)\n   - One period per calendar day\n   - Each day, select top 3 challenges by sort_order and create assignments for eligible players\n\n2. **Weekly Challenges**: `\"weekly:YYYY-Www\"` (ISO week, e.g., `\"weekly:2026-W14\"`)\n   - One period per ISO week\n   - Each week, select top 2 challenges by sort_order\n\n3. **Onboarding**: `\"onboarding\"` (literal, no expiration)\n   - Single lifetime chain per player\n   - No `expires_at` (NULL)\n   - Auto-advances via `prerequisite_id` chain\n\n**Expiration Pattern:**\n- Daily assignments: `expires_at = start of next day (midnight UTC)`\n- Weekly assignments: `expires_at = start of next week (Sunday midnight UTC)`\n- Onboarding: `expires_at = NULL` (no expiration, one-time progression)\n\n---\n\n### **KEY DATABASE ACCESS PATTERNS** (from handlers)\n\n#### **Challenge Progress Evaluation** (`game-settled.ts`)\n```sql\nSELECT ca.id, ca.challenge_id, c.action, c.scope, c.condition, ca.target, ca.progress, \n       ca.status, ca.period_key, c.campaign_id, c.reward_type, c.reward_amount\nFROM challenge_assignments ca\nJOIN challenges c ON c.id = ca.challenge_id\nWHERE ca.user_id = ${userId} AND ca.status = 'active'\n```\nUses index: `idx_assignments_active(user_id, status) WHERE status='active'`\n\n#### **Progress Event Insertion** (idempotent)\n```sql\nINSERT INTO progress_events (assignment_id, round_id, user_id, progress_delta, metadata)\nVALUES (...) ON CONFLICT (assignment_id, round_id) DO NOTHING\n```\n\n#### **Assignment Progress Increment** (atomic)\n```sql\nUPDATE challenge_assignments\nSET progress = progress + ${delta}\nWHERE id = ${assignmentId}\nRETURNING progress\n```\n\n#### **Completion Bonus Check**\n1. Get all active bonuses for campaign\n2. Count `challenge_assignments` WHERE status='completed' AND period_key=X AND campaign_id=Y\n3. If count >= required_count: insert `bonus_completions` (idempotent via UNIQUE)\n\n#### **Onboarding Chain Advancement**\n```sql\nSELECT id, threshold FROM challenges\nWHERE prerequisite_id = ${completedChallengeId} AND is_active = true\nLIMIT 1\n```\nThen insert next assignment with `period_key='onboarding'` (auto-advances on completion)\n\n---\n\n### **IDEMPOTENCY GUARANTEES**\n\nAll reward/progress paths use domain-keyed UNIQUE constraints:\n\n1. **Progress**: `UNIQUE(assignment_id, round_id)` — same round can't increment twice\n2. **Point Grants**: `UNIQUE(user_id, source_type, source_id)` — one grant per source\n3. **Crate Drops**: `UNIQUE(user_id, trigger_type, trigger_id)` — one drop per trigger\n4. **Bonus Completions**: `UNIQUE(user_id, bonus_id, period_key)` — one bonus per period\n5. **Assignment Creation**: `UNIQUE(user_id, challenge_id, period_key)` — one per period\n6. **Pool Fundings**: `UNIQUE(round_id)` — one funding record per settled round\n\n---\n\n### **KEY VERIFICATION ADAPTERS** (`challenge-adapters.ts`)\n\nMap `challenge.action` to game-state evaluation logic:\n\n| Action | Checks | Progress |\n|--------|--------|----------|\n| `game_completed` | Player participated + scope match | +1 |\n| `game_won` | Player won + scope match | +1 |\n| `lobby_filled` | Player created game + scope match | +1 |\n\nAll adapters skip refunded games (when `isWinner === null`).\n\nAll file paths referenced are **absolute paths** as stored in the repository."}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"59720d7a-048c-45e3-b4dd-63ce0cb4da31","uuid":"61c4ce9a-050c-4011-be8d-9e3749288d9c","timestamp":"2026-04-03T20:44:30.738Z","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"I need to understand the challenge engine database schema and seed data. Read these files:\n\n1. `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` - the full migration file with all tables and seeds\n2. Any existing handler files in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/src/queue/handlers/` that interact with challenge_assignments, challenges, campaigns tables - to understand the DB access patterns\n\nFocus on:\n- Table schemas for: campaigns, challenges, challenge_assignments, completion_bonuses, bonus_completions\n- Seed data: what campaigns exist, what challenges exist, what are their sort_orders, how onboarding chain works\n- The period_key format and expiration patterns\n- How assignments are created and queried\n\nRead the actual files thoroughly.","agentId":"ae40d90711f8a806d","agentType":"Explore","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! Now I have a comprehensive understanding. Let me compile a detailed summary of the database schema and seed data:\n\n## Challenge Engine Database Schema & Seed Data Summary\n\nBased on the migration file `/workspaces/rng-utopia/backend/services/backend/migrations/011_challenge_engine.sql` and handler implementations, here's the complete picture:\n\n---\n\n### **TABLE SCHEMAS**\n\n#### **1. Core Campaign & Challenge Tables**\n\n**`campaigns`** — Container for challenge groupings\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `name`: TEXT UNIQUE (e.g., \"Daily Challenges\", \"Weekly Challenges\", \"Onboarding\")\n- `campaign_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('daily', 'weekly', 'onboarding', 'dogpile')\n- `starts_at`, `ends_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (NULL = always active)\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n- `config`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' (type-specific settings)\n\n**`challenges`** — Template definitions for individual challenge tasks\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `title`: TEXT (e.g., \"Play 3 Games\", \"Win a Coinflip\")\n- `description`: TEXT\n- `action`: TEXT (e.g., 'game_completed', 'game_won', 'lobby_filled') — **maps to verification adapters**\n- `scope`: TEXT DEFAULT 'any' CHECK IN ('any', 'coinflip', 'lord', 'closecall') — **game-type filter**\n- `condition`: TEXT DEFAULT 'count' CHECK IN ('count', 'unique_game_types', ...)\n- `threshold`: INT — target value to meet\n- `reward_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'crate')\n- `reward_amount`: INT (for points) or NULL (for crates)\n- `prerequisite_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES challenges(id) — **for onboarding chain linking**\n- `eligible_if`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' (M2+ feature for eligibility rules)\n- `sort_order`: INT DEFAULT 0 — **used to select top 3 daily/top 2 weekly**\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n\n#### **2. Challenge Assignment (Per-Player Period Tracking)**\n\n**`challenge_assignments`** — Player's assignment for a challenge in a specific period\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `challenge_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES challenges(id)\n- `period_key`: TEXT NOT NULL — **date-scoped identifier (see below)**\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'active' CHECK IN ('active', 'completed', 'expired')\n- `progress`: INT DEFAULT 0 — current count toward target\n- `target`: INT NOT NULL — copied from challenge.threshold at assignment time\n- `assigned_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- `expires_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (NULL for onboarding)\n- `completed_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ (when status becomes 'completed')\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, challenge_id, period_key)** — one assignment per player per challenge per period (idempotency guard)\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `idx_assignments_active` ON (user_id, status) WHERE status='active' — **hot query for game.settled**\n- `idx_assignments_period` ON (period_key, status)\n\n#### **3. Progress Tracking**\n\n**`progress_events`** — Audit trail of which game sessions contributed to challenge progress\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `assignment_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES challenge_assignments(id)\n- `round_id`: TEXT NOT NULL — match_id from game.settled event\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `progress_delta`: INT DEFAULT 1 — increment amount\n- `metadata`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' — context (e.g., `{\"game\":\"coinflip\"}`)\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(assignment_id, round_id)** — **idempotency: same round can't count twice**\n\n#### **4. Completion Bonus (Meta-Quest)**\n\n**`completion_bonuses`** — \"Complete all challenges in a period → bonus reward\"\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `title`: TEXT (e.g., \"Daily Bonus Crate\")\n- `description`: TEXT\n- `required_count`: INT (e.g., 3 = \"complete 3 daily challenges\")\n- `reward_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'crate')\n- `reward_amount`: INT (if reward_type='points')\n- `is_active`: BOOLEAN DEFAULT true\n\n**`bonus_completions`** — Per-player bonus completion record\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `bonus_id`: BIGINT NOT NULL REFERENCES completion_bonuses(id)\n- `period_key`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `completed_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, bonus_id, period_key)** — **idempotency: award bonus once per period**\n\n#### **5. Points & Rewards**\n\n**`player_points`** — Running balance of points earned by player\n- `user_id`: TEXT PRIMARY KEY\n- `wallet`: TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE\n- `balance`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — current spendable points\n- `lifetime_earned`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — monotonic aggregate\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`point_grants`** — Immutable ledger of all points awarded\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`, `wallet`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `source_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('wager', 'challenge_completed', 'bonus_completed', 'crate_points')\n- `source_id`: TEXT NOT NULL (round_id, assignment_id, bonus_id, or crate_id)\n- `amount`: BIGINT NOT NULL\n- `metadata`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}' \n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n- **UNIQUE(user_id, source_type, source_id)** — **idempotency key**\n\n**`reward_config`** — Operator-tunable economy parameters\n- `key`: TEXT PRIMARY KEY\n- `value`: TEXT NOT NULL (JSON-encoded)\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`reward_pool`** — Singleton accounting ledger for SOL crate funding\n- `id`: INT PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT 1 (singleton, only one row allowed)\n- `balance_lamports`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — available for SOL crate payouts\n- `lifetime_funded`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — total fees allocated → pool\n- `lifetime_paid`: BIGINT DEFAULT 0 — total SOL paid out via crates\n- `updated_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**`reward_pool_fundings`** — Idempotent pool funding ledger\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `round_id`: TEXT NOT NULL UNIQUE — **one record per settled round**\n- `fee_lamports`: BIGINT NOT NULL (platform fee collected)\n- `funded_lamports`: BIGINT NOT NULL (amount added to pool: fee * fee_share)\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n#### **6. Crate Drops**\n\n**`crate_drops`** — Random loot drop records\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`: TEXT NOT NULL\n- `trigger_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('game_settled', 'challenge_completed', 'bonus_completed')\n- `trigger_id`: TEXT NOT NULL (round_id, assignment_id, or bonus_id)\n- `crate_type`: TEXT CHECK IN ('points', 'sol')\n- `contents_amount`: TEXT NOT NULL (lamports or points as string)\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'pending' CHECK IN ('pending', 'granted', 'failed')\n- `created_at`, `granted_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ\n\n**Indexes:**\n- `idx_crate_drops_user` ON (user_id, created_at DESC)\n- `idx_crate_drops_pending` ON (status) WHERE status='pending'\n\n#### **7. Anti-Abuse & Events**\n\n**`fraud_flags`** — Manual review queue for suspicious activity\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `user_id`, `flag_type`, `related_id`: TEXT\n- `details`: JSONB DEFAULT '{}'\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'open' CHECK IN ('open', 'reviewed', 'dismissed')\n- `created_at`, `resolved_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ\n\n**`dogpile_events`** — Limited-time point multiplier events\n- `id`: BIGINT IDENTITY PRIMARY KEY\n- `campaign_id`: BIGINT REFERENCES campaigns(id)\n- `starts_at`, `ends_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ NOT NULL\n- `multiplier`: NUMERIC(4,2) DEFAULT 2.0\n- `status`: TEXT DEFAULT 'scheduled' CHECK IN ('scheduled', 'active', 'ended', 'cancelled')\n- `created_at`: TIMESTAMPTZ DEFAULT now()\n\n**Index:** `idx_dogpile_active` ON (status, starts_at, ends_at) WHERE status IN ('scheduled', 'active')\n\n---\n\n### **SEED DATA**\n\n#### **1. `reward_config` Defaults**\n```\npoints_per_dollar:          '500'        (e.g., $1 wagered = 500 points)\ndogpile_default_multiplier: '2.0'\nreward_pool_fee_share:      '0.20'       (20% of fees → pool)\npoints_crate_drop_rate:     '0.05'       (5% chance per game)\nsol_crate_drop_rate:        '0.01'       (1% chance per game)\nsol_crate_pool_pct:         '0.10'       (payout = 10% of pool balance)\nsol_crate_min_value:        '10000000'   (100M lamports = ~0.1 SOL threshold)\npoints_crate_min:           '500'\npoints_crate_max:           '5000'\ndaily_challenge_count:      '3'\nweekly_challenge_count:     '2'\n```\n\n#### **2. `campaigns` Seed**\n| id (auto) | name | campaign_type | starts_at | ends_at | is_active |\n|-----------|------|---------------|-----------|---------|-----------|\n| 1 | Daily Challenges | daily | NULL | NULL | true |\n| 2 | Weekly Challenges | weekly | NULL | NULL | true |\n| 3 | Onboarding | onboarding | NULL | NULL | true |\n\n#### **3. `challenges` Seed — Daily Campaign (campaign_id=1)**\n\nCampaigns has 6 daily challenge templates. Top 3 by `sort_order` are assigned to players each day:\n\n| Title | Action | Scope | Condition | Threshold | Reward | sort_order |\n|-------|--------|-------|-----------|-----------|--------|-----------|\n| Play 3 Games | game_completed | any | count | 3 | 100 points | 1 |\n| Win a Coinflip | game_won | coinflip | count | 1 | 150 points | 2 |\n| Fill a Lobby | lobby_filled | any | count | 1 | 200 points | 3 |\n| Play 5 Games | game_completed | any | count | 5 | 250 points | 4 |\n| Win 3 Games | game_won | any | count | 3 | 300 points | 5 |\n| Try Close Call | game_completed | closecall | count | 1 | 150 points | 6 |\n\n**Daily Completion Bonus (campaign_id=1):**\n- required_count: 3, reward_type: 'crate'\n\n#### **4. `challenges` Seed — Weekly Campaign (campaign_id=2)**\n\n6 weekly challenge templates. Top 2 by `sort_order` are assigned per week:\n\n| Title | Action | Scope | Condition | Threshold | Reward | sort_order |\n|-------|--------|-------|-----------|-----------|--------|-----------|\n| Play 20 Games | game_completed | any | count | 20 | 1000 points | 1 |\n| Win 10 Games | game_won | any | count | 10 | 1500 points | 2 |\n| Play Every Game Type | game_completed | any | unique_game_types | 3 | 2000 points | 3 |\n| Fill 5 Lobbies | lobby_filled | any | count | 5 | 1200 points | 4 |\n\n#### **5. `challenges` Seed — Onboarding Campaign (campaign_id=3)**\n\n3-step chain linked via `prerequisite_id`:\n\n**Step 1 (sort_order=1, prerequisite_id=NULL):**\n- Title: \"Play Your First Game\"\n- Action: game_completed, Scope: any, Threshold: 1, Reward: 1000 points\n\n**Step 2 (sort_order=2, prerequisite_id=Step1.id):**\n- Title: \"Win a Game\"\n- Action: game_won, Scope: any, Threshold: 1, Reward: 1500 points\n\n**Step 3 (sort_order=3, prerequisite_id=Step2.id):**\n- Title: \"Try All 3 Game Types\"\n- Action: game_completed, Scope: any, Condition: unique_game_types, Threshold: 3, Reward: 2500 points\n\n#### **6. `reward_pool` Seed**\n```\nINSERT INTO reward_pool (id, balance_lamports, lifetime_funded, lifetime_paid)\nVALUES (1, 0, 0, 0);\n```\n\n---\n\n### **PERIOD_KEY FORMAT & EXPIRATION**\n\nFrom integration tests, the `period_key` structure is:\n\n1. **Daily Challenges**: `\"daily:YYYY-MM-DD\"` (e.g., `\"daily:2026-04-03\"`)\n   - One period per calendar day\n   - Each day, select top 3 challenges by sort_order and create assignments for eligible players\n\n2. **Weekly Challenges**: `\"weekly:YYYY-Www\"` (ISO week, e.g., `\"weekly:2026-W14\"`)\n   - One period per ISO week\n   - Each week, select top 2 challenges by sort_order\n\n3. **Onboarding**: `\"onboarding\"` (literal, no expiration)\n   - Single lifetime chain per player\n   - No `expires_at` (NULL)\n   - Auto-advances via `prerequisite_id` chain\n\n**Expiration Pattern:**\n- Daily assignments: `expires_at = start of next day (midnight UTC)`\n- Weekly assignments: `expires_at = start of next week (Sunday midnight UTC)`\n- Onboarding: `expires_at = NULL` (no expiration, one-time progression)\n\n---\n\n### **KEY DATABASE ACCESS PATTERNS** (from handlers)\n\n#### **Challenge Progress Evaluation** (`game-settled.ts`)\n```sql\nSELECT ca.id, ca.challenge_id, c.action, c.scope, c.condition, ca.target, ca.progress, \n       ca.status, ca.period_key, c.campaign_id, c.reward_type, c.reward_amount\nFROM challenge_assignments ca\nJOIN challenges c ON c.id = ca.challenge_id\nWHERE ca.user_id = ${userId} AND ca.status = 'active'\n```\nUses index: `idx_assignments_active(user_id, status) WHERE status='active'`\n\n#### **Progress Event Insertion** (idempotent)\n```sql\nINSERT INTO progress_events (assignment_id, round_id, user_id, progress_delta, metadata)\nVALUES (...) ON CONFLICT (assignment_id, round_id) DO NOTHING\n```\n\n#### **Assignment Progress Increment** (atomic)\n```sql\nUPDATE challenge_assignments\nSET progress = progress + ${delta}\nWHERE id = ${assignmentId}\nRETURNING progress\n```\n\n#### **Completion Bonus Check**\n1. Get all active bonuses for campaign\n2. Count `challenge_assignments` WHERE status='completed' AND period_key=X AND campaign_id=Y\n3. If count >= required_count: insert `bonus_completions` (idempotent via UNIQUE)\n\n#### **Onboarding Chain Advancement**\n```sql\nSELECT id, threshold FROM challenges\nWHERE prerequisite_id = ${completedChallengeId} AND is_active = true\nLIMIT 1\n```\nThen insert next assignment with `period_key='onboarding'` (auto-advances on completion)\n\n---\n\n### **IDEMPOTENCY GUARANTEES**\n\nAll reward/progress paths use domain-keyed UNIQUE constraints:\n\n1. **Progress**: `UNIQUE(assignment_id, round_id)` — same round can't increment twice\n2. **Point Grants**: `UNIQUE(user_id, source_type, source_id)` — one grant per source\n3. **Crate Drops**: `UNIQUE(user_id, trigger_type, trigger_id)` — one drop per trigger\n4. **Bonus Completions**: `UNIQUE(user_id, bonus_id, period_key)` — one bonus per period\n5. **Assignment Creation**: `UNIQUE(user_id, challenge_id, period_key)` — one per period\n6. **Pool Fundings**: `UNIQUE(round_id)` — one funding record per settled round\n\n---\n\n### **KEY VERIFICATION ADAPTERS** (`challenge-adapters.ts`)\n\nMap `challenge.action` to game-state evaluation logic:\n\n| Action | Checks | Progress |\n|--------|--------|----------|\n| `game_completed` | Player participated + scope match | +1 |\n| `game_won` | Player won + scope match | +1 |\n| `lobby_filled` | Player created game + scope match | +1 |\n\nAll adapters skip refunded games (when `isWinner === null`).\n\nAll file paths referenced are **absolute paths** as stored in the repository."}],"totalDurationMs":119998,"totalTokens":67701,"totalToolUseCount":29,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":6988,"cache_read_input_tokens":56215,"output_tokens":4498,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":6988},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
